sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MRREST as Model Registry REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Model Registry REST API Access via Route
        Client->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token (JWT)
        Router->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS reencrypt<br/>Bearer Token (JWT)
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Token validated
        KRBP->>MRREST: HTTP/8080<br/>No auth (validated by proxy)
        MRREST->>PG: PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Configurable TLS<br/>Username/Password
        PG-->>MRREST: Query results
        MRREST-->>KRBP: REST response
        KRBP-->>Router: HTTPS response
        Router-->>Client: HTTPS response
    end

    participant Operator as Model Registry Operator
    participant OSConfig as config.openshift.io<br/>Ingress
    participant AuthCR as Platform Auth CR<br/>services.platform.opendatahub.io

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Operator,AuthCR: Flow 2: Operator Reconciliation
        Operator->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Watch ModelRegistry CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: CR change events
        Operator->>OSConfig: HTTPS/443<br/>Read cluster ingress domain<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        OSConfig-->>Operator: Ingress config
        Operator->>AuthCR: HTTPS/443<br/>Read admin groups<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        AuthCR-->>Operator: Admin group config
        Operator->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Create/Update managed resources<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    end

    participant MigMgr as StorageMigrationManager
    participant MigAPI as migration.k8s.io API

    rect rgb(248, 255, 240)
        Note over MigMgr,MigAPI: Flow 3: Storage Version Migration
        MigMgr->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Check CRD StoredVersions<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>MigMgr: CRD status
        alt Kubernetes StorageVersionMigration available
            MigMgr->>MigAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Create StorageVersionMigration<br/>ServiceAccount Token
            MigAPI-->>MigMgr: Migration status
        else Fallback: Manual migration
            MigMgr->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>List all ModelRegistry CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
            K8sAPI-->>MigMgr: ModelRegistry list
            MigMgr->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Re-write each CR (triggers conversion)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        end
    end
